member_list

member_list.Rd

Chicago R User Group Data downloaded from meetup.com/ChicagoRUG. PII removed, data formated and ready for analysis.

data(member_list)

Format

A data.frame with 3606 observations on 16 variables:

  • Member.ID: Integer. Original Member.ID overwritten with a sequence of numbers beginning with 1 (not zero). Used as count index to sum new members.

  • Location: Character string, format by "City, State"

  • Joined.Group.on: Date, format YYYY-MM-DD

  • Last.visited.group.on: Date, format YYYY-MM-DD

  • Last.Attended: Date, format YYYY-MM-DD

  • Total.RSVPs: Integer

  • RSVPed.Yes: Integer

  • RSVPed.Maybe: Integer

  • RSVPed.No: Integer

  • Meetups.attended: Integer

  • No.shows: Integer

  • Intro: Factor with 2 levels. "Yes","No"

  • Photo: Factor with 2 levels. "Yes","No"

  • Assistant.Organizer: Factor with 2 levels. "Yes","No"

  • Mailing.List: Factor with 3 levels. "Yes","No", "Digest"

  • R.Experience: Character string, member input on signup.

Source

https://www.meetup.com/ChicagoRUG/members/?op=csv
